FBIS3-13678 "drnes053_l_94007" FBIS-NES-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Waqf Closes Temple Mount to Non-Muslims TA1803055194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0500 GMT 18 Mar 94 TA1803055194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] The waqf, the Islamic trust in charge of Muslim shrines, has decided not to allow non-Muslims to enter the Temple Mount. Waqf spokesman 'Adnan al-Husayni said the decision was taken because the police have damaged the right of freedom of religion by placing limitations on the age and numbers of worshipers allowed to enter the Temple Mount. [passage omitted]
